name: FREEDOM
description:
Insights from the Dreaming Pool - Move, twist, free yourself.

Break free, shift, move, loosen out of whatever it is, keep going. don’t give up, you can do it. 
What does freedom mean for you?
Freedom to be who you are, freedom to say what you want, freedom to stay quiet, freedom to follow what’s right for you, freedom to follow your own path, freedom from oppression, freedom from your own constraints - Freedom.

Shake it up, shake it loose, move out, move on, detach, break free. 

In the image of this card there is someone or something exerting itself to free themselves from the structure they are currently ensconced in. There is a need. It is time for you to release yourself from the limitations of your current structure whether it be physical or mental or both. No matter 
how beautiful your structure is it no longer serves you. Take what you have learned from it and move on. Move from side to side, squirm your way out. If you have to squeeze and push then do it. 
When you’re free jump around and move on down the road. Feel the joy of freedom, the release, the correctness, the flexibility and the peace.

The Dreaming Pool Oracle is a collaboration between artists Maia Mellier 🕸 🕷 (@maiamellier) & AEVIN (@aevin_io)
